---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="소개 | DevArchive" description="시스템 설계와 인간 중심의 의도에 대해 고민합니다.">
  <main>
    <!-- Immersive Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative h-screen w-full flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-black">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img id="hero-bg" class="parallax-bg w-full h-[120%] object-cover object-center opacity-80" alt="Minimalist workspace" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBSMObE4-VS8328-PH8V3FwxP39zgM7dIDDXwYuUCB384uShdjRcxXeU62k1VlccJWgpr9nmxF8XBKAIBOCM_e9sSwRMYYYYwVs2nljhymuHrRdv4HKQRwMi2FkqbmKpGIfBeABUXnrU52dDEqBEXYX7kM3UEp9KLq-D6XGMEwOtxbvMYb1o_ZLdQz0_2NJen2Y_paMoAS7QayCOAXo3sHpIgWfztrLgK_cuPqZGshaNafrBzYCayMgYGd9D2fCbwL4iVWUB9Zf5iFh"/>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>
      </div>
      <div id="hero-text" class="relative z-10 max-w-[900px] mx-auto text-center px-6 transition-transform duration-75">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] tracking-[0.2em] font-semibold uppercase text-white/80 mb-6 block">The Narrative</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-8 leading-[1.05] break-keep">
          의도를 코드로 엮어내는<br/>소프트웨어 아키텍트.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed break-keep">
          단순한 구현을 넘어 인간 중심의 경험과 시스템의 안정성을 고민합니다.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- Scroll Indicator -->
      <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-10 animate-bounce-subtle">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white/60 text-3xl">keyboard_arrow_down</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="bg-apple-background dark:bg-apple-darkBackground pt-24 transition-colors">
      <!-- Essay Content -->
      <section class="max-w-[700px] mx-auto px-6 mb-32">
        <div class="space-y-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-apple-textMuted dark:text-apple-darkTextMuted">
          <p class="reveal-up first-letter:text-7xl first-letter:font-bold first-letter:mr-3 first-letter:float-left first-letter:text-apple-text dark:first-letter:text-apple-darkText">
            소프트웨어는 단순한 명령어의 나열이 아닙니다. 그것은 설계자의 의도가 만나는 디지털 캔버스이자 훌륭한 표현 수단이라고 생각합니다. 저의 여정은 단순히 키보드를 두드리는 것에서 시작하지 않았습니다. 여러 조각들이 어떻게 맞아떨어져 하나의 응집력 있는 전체를 만들어내는지에 대한 순수한 호기심에서 출발했습니다.
          </p>
          <p class="reveal-up stagger-1">
            지난 몇 년 동안 저는 간단한 웹사이트 구축부터 복잡한 분산 시스템 아키텍처 설계에 이르기까지 다양한 기술적 전환기를 겪어왔습니다. 하지만 제 철학은 언제나 변함이 없었습니다. '화려함보다는 명확성(Clarity above cleverness)'. 제대로 작성된 코드 블록은 한 편의 잘 짜인 산문처럼 이어져야 하며, 예측 가능하고 우아하며 목적이 뚜렷해야 합니다.
          </p>
          <div class="pt-6 reveal-up stagger-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText mb-4">단순함(Simplicity)을 향한 여정</h3>
            <p>
              때때로 무의미한 복잡성을 치켜세우는 IT 업계 속에서, 저는 "조용한(Quiet)" 인터페이스에 끌립니다. 시선을 강탈하지 않으면서도 온전히 가치를 전달하는 것들 말이죠. 이 개발 블로그는 고도의 효율성을 추구하는 엔지니어링과 인간 중심적 디자인의 따뜻함이 만나는 교차점에 대한 저만의 큐레이션 공간입니다.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Tech Stack Grid (Restored Original Clean Format) -->
      <section class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 mb-40">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal-up">
          <span class="text-[0.75rem] tracking-[0.08em] font-medium uppercase text-apple-textMuted dark:text-apple-darkTextMuted mb-2 block">Toolbox</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">Modern Architectures</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-up stagger-1 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-px bg-apple-border/40 dark:bg-apple-darkBorder/40 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-apple-border/40 dark:border-apple-darkBorder/40">
          <div class="bg-apple-surface dark:bg-apple-darkSurface p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 hover:bg-apple-background dark:hover:bg-black transition-colors duration-300">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl opacity-60 text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">code</span>
            <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">TypeScript</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-apple-surface dark:bg-apple-darkSurface p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 hover:bg-apple-background dark:hover:bg-black transition-colors duration-300">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl opacity-60 text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">layers</span>
            <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">React</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-apple-surface dark:bg-apple-darkSurface p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 hover:bg-apple-background dark:hover:bg-black transition-colors duration-300">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl opacity-60 text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">database</span>
            <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">PostgreSQL</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-apple-surface dark:bg-apple-darkSurface p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 hover:bg-apple-background dark:hover:bg-black transition-colors duration-300">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl opacity-60 text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">terminal</span>
            <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">Node.js</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-apple-surface dark:bg-apple-darkSurface p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 hover:bg-apple-background dark:hover:bg-black transition-colors duration-300">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl opacity-60 text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">cloud</span>
            <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">AWS</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-apple-surface dark:bg-apple-darkSurface p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 hover:bg-apple-background dark:hover:bg-black transition-colors duration-300">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl opacity-60 text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">brush</span>
            <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">Tailwind</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Timeline Section (Restored Original Clean Format) -->
      <section class="max-w-[700px] mx-auto px-6 pb-32">
        <div class="mb-16 reveal-up">
          <span class="text-[0.75rem] tracking-[0.08em] font-medium uppercase text-apple-textMuted dark:text-apple-darkTextMuted mb-2 block">The Timeline</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText">주요 여정</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-16 relative">
          <!-- Vertical Line -->
          <div class="absolute left-[3px] top-2 bottom-2 w-[1px] bg-apple-border dark:bg-apple-darkBorder"></div>
          
          <div class="relative pl-10 reveal-up stagger-1">
            <div class="absolute left-0 top-2.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-apple-text dark:bg-apple-darkText ring-4 ring-apple-background dark:ring-apple-darkBackground"></div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-bold text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText mb-1 block">2026 ~ 현재</span>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText mb-2">SSAFY 15기 이수</h4>
              <p class="text-apple-textMuted dark:text-apple-darkTextMuted leading-relaxed break-keep">급성장하는 핀테크 스타트업에서 코어 경험(Core Experience) 팀을 리드하며 성능 최적화와 디자인 시스템 구축에 집중하고 있습니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative pl-10 reveal-up stagger-2">
            <div class="absolute left-0 top-2.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-apple-textMuted dark:bg-apple-darkTextMuted ring-4 ring-apple-background dark:ring-apple-darkBackground"></div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-bold text-apple-textMuted dark:text-apple-darkTextMuted mb-1 block">2024 ~ 2026</span>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-apple-text dark:text-apple-darkText mb-2">국립한밭대학교 졸업</h4>
              <p class="text-apple-textMuted dark:text-apple-darkTextMuted leading-relaxed break-keep">인터랙션 디자인과 프론트엔드 엔지니어링의 교차점에 집중하며 인터랙티브 에이전시 소속으로 AWWWARDS 등에서 개발 성과를 다수 수상했습니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', () => {
      // 1. Immersive Parallax Hero
      const heroBg = document.getElementById("hero-bg");
      const heroText = document.getElementById("hero-text");
      
      const onScrollHero = () => {
        const scrolled = window.scrollY;
        
        if (scrolled < window.innerHeight && heroBg && heroText) {
          heroBg.style.transform = `translateY(${scrolled * 0.4}px)`;
          heroText.style.transform = `translateY(${scrolled * 0.15}px)`;
          heroText.style.opacity = (1 - (scrolled / (window.innerHeight * 0.6))).toString();
        }
      };

      window.addEventListener("scroll", onScrollHero, { passive: true });

      // 2. Smooth Intersection Observer for Scroll Reveals
      const revealOptions = {
        root: null,
        rootMargin: '0px 0px -50px 0px',
        threshold: 0.1
      };

      const revealObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries, observer) => {
        entries.forEach(entry => {
          if (entry.isIntersecting) {
            entry.target.classList.add("active");
            observer.unobserve(entry.target);
          }
        });
      }, revealOptions);

      document.querySelectorAll(".reveal-up").forEach(el => {
        revealObserver.observe(el);
      });
    });
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
